    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((0.02 / 0.40))
    v2 = 0.13
    tmp = (v2 - ((v0 + 0.02 * v0 + 0.03) + v0))
    v0 = (0.79 - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.47) / (v0 + 0.92 - v0 + 0.86)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = 0.49
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.52) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.85)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v1 + 0.34 + v2 + 0.54)))
    data[tid] = v0
